      • wandCheck

        public static double wandCheck(org.bukkit.entity.Player player)
        Checks what kind of wand a player holds. Returns a value based on the wand and it's relation to the player.
        Parameters:
        player - - Player being checked. The player must be holding a wand.
        Returns:
        2 - The wand is not your type AND/OR is not allied to you.

        1 - The wand is your type and is allied to you OR the wand is the elder wand and is not allied to you.

        0.5 - The wand is the elder wand and it is allied to you.
